contentrichtext.text: '''Lelu''' or '''Lelu Town''' is a municipality of the state of [[Kosrae]], in the [[Federated States of Micronesia]]. The municipality of Lelu consists of [[Lelu Island]] (a small satellite island of Kosrae Island) and a big part of the northeastern portion of [[Kosrae Island]]. Its capital is ''Lelu Village'', located on Lelu island. Another village in the municipality, on Kosrae Island, is [[Tofol]], the capital of the state of Kosrae. Established as a Town since Jan. 1989.
